<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Roadcorp lifts yr shr, no div.</title>
<headline>Roadcorp lifts yr shr, no div.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-10-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended July 31 1996</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)    15.10	vs    10.10</p>
<p>    Net income		3.63	vs    1.52</p>
<p>    Interest paid	   6.00	vs    1.21</p>
<p>    Turnover		 82.13	vs    9.71</p>
<p>Full name:  Roadcorp Ltd (industrial-transportation)</p>
<p>NOTE - The directors are confident that turnover and earnings will increase further in the current year due to the improved use of facilities and operating assets.</p>
<p>The group intends holding a rights offer to reduce debt and finance further growth.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
